  处理器              AMD Ryzen 9 3900X 12-Core
  主板                华硕 PRIME X570-P ( AMD PCI 标准主机 CPU 桥 )...</Run>
                                                    </Paragraph>
                                                </FlowDocument>
                                            </RichTextBox>
                                        </Grid>

                                        <!-- 分割线 -->
                                        <GridSplitter Grid.Column="1" Height="1" VerticalAlignment="Bottom" HorizontalAlignment="Stretch" Background="Gray" />
                                    </Grid>
                                </ListBoxItem>
                            </ListBox>
